             was indicted for <rs id="t17860222-67-off359" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17860222-67-off359" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860222-67-off359" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17860222-67-cd360" type="crimeDate">23d day of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860222-67-off359 t17860222-67-cd360"></join> last, one linen bag, value 3 d. a cloth waistcoat, value 1 s. a pair of breeches, value 1 s. 6 d. two shirts, value 4 s. two pair of stockings, value 2 s. a pair of boot stockings, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17860222-67-victim782" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Shelley
                  <interp inst="t17860222-67-victim782" type="surname" value="Shelley"></interp>
